    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>After reading the Rhubarb recipe and other comments, thought I would ask the bloggers if anyone out there has a recipe for Rhubarb scones.  I have gone through every search engine I can think of and can&#8217;t find one.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-2117' data-commentid="2117" data-postid="1745" data-belowelement="comment-2117" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to rinilini" aria-label='Reply to rinilini'>Reply</a>    </div>
