      <a href="https://orangette.net/2005/05/rhubarb-better-late-than-never-and-right-on-time/#comment-2122"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-03-07T10:10:41-05:00">Monday, March 7, 2011 at 10:10 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dear Molly,</p>
<p>I like the idea of baking the rhubard and also adding the orange zest. My mother (may she rest in peace) used to pair the rhubard with strawberries and make either a compote or a pie and this helped cut down on the sugar. The rhubard and strawberries are a natural together.</p>
    </div>

